'''Gambit Esports''' is a CIS team.

== History ==

=== Formation ===
'''Gambit Esports''', originally '''Gambit Gaming.CIS''', was announced on January 12, 2016 after the organization [[Gambit Gaming]] sold its [[League Championship Series/Europe/2016 Season/Spring Season|European LCS]] seed. Though initially the team contained no players from their previous European roster, former [[Gambit Gaming]] jungler [[Diamondprox]] joined in February when he became unable to compete with [[Unicorns of Love]] in the LCS due to visa issues. In June 2017, a second Gambit EU LCS veteran – support [[Edward]] – rejoined, while the team also added mid laner [[Kira]] and top laner [[PvPStejos]] from Worlds quarterfinalists [[M19]] (formerly [[Albus NoX Luna]]).

